{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Jews were being brought to Warsaw from little towns around because once all those people already then coming with or pushing their little carts or with, with their possessions with all kinds of, of, of bits and pieces, mattresses and beds and so on.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they were already being brought from elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they were forced out of there-- because-- that was later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Became-- later in 1940, became-- and probably later in 1941, the Jews were concentrated in bigger places.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was one of the-- of the-- main, main things things, main points of the policy which later was an extermination policy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One had to concentrate them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in Warsaw, Jews from little towns and villages around Warsaw in quite a big radius were brought there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know really-- not from everywhere because obviously there were little towns near Warsaw where there were little ghettos on their own, like [NON-ENGLISH] I know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But quite a lot of were brought to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what happened was that-- what I remember is that I even wrote a little cartoon story all drawn and written by me about the adventures of a Jew who has to go to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That must have been later in 1940 about how it starts that he's-- that the-- the-- the Germans come to his flat and say, Juden raus.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You understand what the word, yes?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes, means Jews out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out, And then he's getting his possessions together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he's-- this-- and he comes down and, and boys shout at him some kind of-- something like little Jew, just pejorative in Polish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he loses his things, and then he's beaten by the policeman and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally he goes to the ghetto, and he says, finally, I'm in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
